- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper may touch upon security concerns related to financial transactions in rural and semi-urban areas. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses the use of IoT and Mobility, which are related to networking and internet architecture. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper may discuss the social networks and information flow related to financial inclusion projects in rural and semi-urban areas.
